+# Velocity Riders 3D (Concept + Playable Web Prototype)
+
+This repository now contains a **high-fidelity concept prototype** for **Velocity Riders 3D**, a realistic + arcade hybrid bike-racing game vision targeting:
+
+- Android
+- iOS
+- Web
+
+## What is included
+
+- A playable browser prototype (`index.html`) with:
+  - cinematic HUD
+  - high-speed pseudo-3D bike racing feel
+  - nitro boost
+  - multiple environment themes
+  - dynamic weather toggle
+  - camera mode switch
+- A production blueprint section covering:
+  - bike system and in-game economy
+  - multiplayer/backend architecture
+  - progression/live ops strategy
+
+## Quick start
+
+Open `index.html` in a browser.
+
+### Controls
+
+- `↑` accelerate
+- `←` / `→` steer
+- `Space` nitro
+
+## Recommended full production stack
+
+- **Engine:** Unity 3D (URP/HDRP mobile profile) or Unreal Engine 5
+- **Multiplayer:** Photon Fusion
+- **Backend:** Firebase or Supabase
+- **Audio:** FMOD or Wwise
+- **Monetization:** AdMob + Stripe/Razorpay (region dependent)
+
+## Next milestones
+
+1. Move prototype logic into Unity/UE project.
+2. Implement modular bike physics controller (wheelie + drift + traction curves).
+3. Add full garage/store/economy loop.
+4. Implement matchmaking and dedicated multiplayer race flow.
+5. Add live progression systems (XP, missions, tournaments).
 
